 [162.5, 1315.6, 1091.0, 1336.5]}, {"text": "While the study gives appropriate consideration to recent fund performance and historical returns, the assumption", "bbox": [162.5, 1340.6, 1111.5, 1361.5]}, {"text": "is primarily a long-term, prospective rate.", "bbox": [162.5, 1365.6, 509.9, 1386.5]}, {"text": "The Company’s discount rate assumptions are derived from a range of factors, including a yield curve for", "bbox": [214.6, 1408.2, 1096.2, 1429.1]}, {"text": "certain plans, composed of the rates of return on high-quality fixed-income corporate bonds available at the", "bbox": [162.5, 1433.2, 1059.9, 1454.1]}, {"text": "112", "bbox": [621.9, 1484.1, 653.1, 1504.9]}]}